  /                                                                                    \
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                                                        |
|                             -------- Welcome ! --------                                |
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|     This is our Raytracer : The goal of this project is to generate a picture          |
|     which has been calculated by Raytracing.                                           |
|                                                                                        |
|     To use our Raytracer you can do this : ./rt your_config_file                       |
|     With your_config_file, being simply your config file !                             |
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|     You can add arguments after your_config_file :                                     |
|                                                                                        |
|     - You can put the number of threads which you want to use : 1, 2, 3, 4.            |
|                                                                                        |
|     - After the number of threads, you can add the name of the bmp file you want       |
|       to export your image, but you just can use it with one threads.                  |
|                                                                                        |
|     - To use our config file  : read the next Totem !                                  |
|                                                                                        |
 \ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _  /
  \                                                                                    /
   \/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/
