    /- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - \
   /\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\/\  
  /                                                                                    \
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|                             One line equal one object !                                |
|                                                                                        |
| You can put :										 |
|											 |
|  x_pos : Position on the X axis							 |
|  y_pos : Position on the Y axis							 |
|  z_pos : Position on the Z axis							 |
|  Radius : The radius of your object							 |
|  Shine : How shiny your object is, added to the light					 |
|  Red/Green/blue : The color of your object                                             |
|											 |	
|  Here is an example of a config file:			                                 |
|   sphere:pos_x;pos_y;pos_z;radius;shine;red;green;blue;                                |
|   cylindre:pos_x;pos_y;pos_z;radius;shine;red;green;blue;ang_x;ang_y;ang_z;z_min;z_max;|
|   cone:pos_x;pos_y;pos_z;ang_cone;shine;red;green;blue;ang_x;ang_y;ang_z;z_min;z_max;  |
|   plan:pos_x;pos_y;pos_z;shine;red;green;blue;ang_x;ang_y;ang_z;radius_min;radius_max; |
|   spot:pos_x;pos_y;pos_z;red;green;blue;                                               |
|   paraboloide:pos_x;pos_y;pos_z;CSTE;shine;red;green;blue;ang_x;ang_y;ang_z;z_min;z_max|
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|                                                                                        |
|             Don't put an empty line and respect this syntax !                          |
|                                                                                        |
|                       THANK YOU FOR USING OUR PROGRAM !                                |
| Journet Quentin / Loverg Clement / Casier Sofian / Koszyczek Laurent / Amoureux Alix   |
